{"tid":1656838,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"死因有無可疑？","createTime":"2019-10-15T20:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T21:43:33.000Z","uid":219147,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"59b83cac40dbf9ae577ac54fb1532bda08fe13eb","tid":1656838,"uid":219147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T20:48:52.000Z","msg":"由九月開始，每逢香港發現屍體，都有網民擔心死者係「被自殺」，部份矛頭更直指警方。上月底喺油塘對開海面發現的全裸女浮屍近日更惹來全城關注，死者同學在校內示威，要求校方交出CCTV證死者死因。一時間，傳聞甚囂塵上。<br />\n<br />\n究竟本港有屍體被發現後，一般係點樣處理？警方將案件列作有無可疑，會唔會影響驗屍程序？前線突發記者、救護員、法醫、殯儀業人員對近日嘅屍體發現案又有咩睇法？ 坊間的質疑，又有無理據？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ESVaYv2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FESVaYv2.png&h=1a358b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/371653272981177/posts/1865559993590490?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F371653272981177%2Fposts%2F1865559993590490%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLC8lxPyN12Ak3mY6G5vlvHI%3D&h=a26a50e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/371653272981177/posts/1865559993590490?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n某程度同意記者話屍體發現唔算特別多<br />\n因為事實香港地自殺真係經常有<br />\n只係呢段時間特別多人留意<br />\n但當中短時間幾單係浮屍或海邊發現<br />\n呢樣真係好難唔令人覺得冇問題喎<br />\n法醫講得好啱<br />\n理應繼續調查才合理"},{"pid":"a21105c75781c85e1e3af10df925537fb440fdbc","tid":1656838,"uid":219147,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T21:43:33.000Z","msg":"港聞<br />\n資深法醫「馬宣立」：陳彥霖浮屍全裸有可疑 警方應公開更多調查資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1iTcaK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1iTcaK.jpg&h=31978352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://jojo01.me/view2/54492/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c